01:24:36,534 --> 01:24:38,369
Here's what we'll do.

774
01:24:38,453 --> 01:24:45,376
As soon as I ask him to change the lease
and he says no, just shoot his ass dead.

775
01:24:45,459 --> 01:24:49,630
- Why me?
- I'm all out of bullets.

776
01:24:56,095 --> 01:25:02,393
Howard, it's good to hear from you too.
What do you want from me? Spit it out.

777
01:25:05,312 --> 01:25:08,816
Listen, Howard,
I'm not interested in the Third World.

778
01:25:08,899 --> 01:25:11,902
Too much can go the wrong way
and not much can go our way.

779
01:25:11,986 --> 01:25:15,239
We've had this discussion.
I don't ever want to have it again.

780
01:25:15,364 --> 01:25:19,827
Say hello to your wife.
You're married, aren't you?

781
01:25:23,706 --> 01:25:27,501
Lookin' for Chance Wilder. You him?

782
01:25:31,005 --> 01:25:32,089
