So that's the end of that story.

796
01:26:21,888 --> 01:26:28,145
So if you came here to kill me, do it now.
If not, get the fuck outta here.

797
01:26:28,228 --> 01:26:33,650
I don't have the time to play with
guys like you, OK? I'm very busy.

798
01:26:34,734 --> 01:26:35,986
This ain't a game.

799
01:26:36,111 --> 01:26:39,239
All business is a game
one way or another.

800
01:26:39,281 --> 01:26:43,076
- Sellin' drugs ain't no game.
- It's not your average game.

801
01:26:43,159 --> 01:26:48,164
I make $500,000 a year to sit
in this office and run this bank, OK?

802
01:26:48,206 --> 01:26:54,170
I make another $50 million a year to sit
in the same office and run those drugs.

803
01:26:54,254 --> 01:26:57,173
Now, that's a big game and it's big time.

804
01:26:57,257 --> 01:27:01,344
The game's over.
Go ahead and do it, Marlboro.

805
01:27:16,818 --> 01:27:20,613
What are you waitin' for?
Kill him and let's get outta here.

806
01:27:24,951 --> 01:27:27,036
