807
01:27:30,373 --> 01:27:32,125
It's not right.

808
01:27:32,208 --> 01:27:36,879
Hey, this scumbag killed
four of our friends just for laughs.

809
01:27:36,963 --> 01:27:39,048
Still doesn't make it right.

810
01:27:39,132 --> 01:27:41,551
What are you talkin' about?

811
01:27:42,844 --> 01:27:46,722
My old man used to tell me,
before he left this shitty world,

812
01:27:46,806 --> 01:27:48,891
never shoot an unarmed man.

813
01:27:48,975 --> 01:27:51,060
Fuck your old man. He's dead.

814
01:27:51,143 --> 01:27:54,063
Leave my old man out of this, all right?

815
01:27:55,815 --> 01:27:59,652
- Now he's armed.
- That gun's empty, Harley.

816
01:28:00,820 --> 01:28:05,491
So what? This piece of shit
