just gonna walk in here and shoot me?

819
01:28:22,925 --> 01:28:27,263
- You thought that, didn't you?
- That was the plan.

820
01:28:28,514 --> 01:28:30,599
Yeah, that was the plan.

821
01:28:30,683 --> 01:28:34,520
You guys, you guys are a piece of work.

822
01:28:34,603 --> 01:28:38,274
You got an edge.
And I like that. I do. I like that.

823
01:28:38,357 --> 01:28:44,613
